Class definition:
1) Avoid state as a variable
2) Always a fn has a return type
3) class member variables are to be private without a valid reason otherwise

Question: What is the size of given below struct. Why?
struct{
int a;
char b;
int c;
char d;
}

ANS (from all) : 10bytes because int is 4bytes and char is 1byte => 2(4)+2(1)= 10
